{"tid":2006473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[舊聞重溫]5月11日嘅內會沖突","createTime":"2020-05-07T19:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T20:25:28.000Z","uid":353351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a00ae4922d163c22e819f413ead811d6ec945bbf","tid":2006473,"uid":353351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:58:27.000Z","msg":"搵翻段舊文俾大家睇睇<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5月11日</span></span></strong><br />\n原文：《影像現場：《逃犯條例》修訂法案委員會「鬧雙胞」 泛民建制議員爆發衝突》 <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20190511-photo-legco-fugitive-ordinance/?utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20190511-photo-legco-fugitive-ordinance%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dcopy&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0IbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=8d0201b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20190511-photo-legco-fugitive-ordinance/?utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>.<br />\n.<br />\n.</strong></div><br />\n自5月10日夜晚，民主派議員留守立法會。5月11日早上8時半，民主黨涂謹申召開會議，而建制派支持的經民聯石禮謙則於早上 9 時開始主持會議，地點同樣是立法會會議室 1。根據立法會安排，今次是法案委員會第三次會議。多名建制派議員進入會議室後，石禮謙在多名建制派護擁下嘗試以咪發言，但隨即被泛民議員包圍，「不要再破壞立法會」，現場情況混亂。其後石禮謙宣布會議暫停，部分建制派人員退出會議室 1。新同盟范國威倒地，救護員到場以擔架抬走送院，民主派議員則指范國威曾被推撞<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EM9OHp0VAAArMZk?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEM9OHp0VAAArMZk%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=9c1b6e91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依一刻，我仍然會對議會同道寄於信任。但果無力阻止，到強推國歌法嗰一刻，要面對嘅將會係比612更血腥嘅鎮壓，請諸君做好進擊及被槍殺嘅準備。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無論點，聽日請關注內會同支持郭榮鏗</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7187422d8baced5a26ec0b440be66a98aac077a8","tid":2006473,"uid":353351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T20:02:43.000Z","msg":"試推"},{"pid":"4f233c4346f786d88e941dc42e3c42321903e044","tid":2006473,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T20:25:28.000Z","msg":"聽日請關注內會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}